column5: hahah Thats insane ! I guess nets wouldn't work ? haha
I would love to give that a good but don't think they fish them that way any more.
Backbreaking fishing I would think. Those fish are going nuts! Kenny G.

You should come deep sea bottom fishing with me sometime 'enry... I'd like to see how much spunk you had left in you after pulling a 30lb. Grouper up out of 200 FOW!!!... and that's just the warm up!... Then we'll move to the Amberjack hole!!!  Did I mention the blistering sun???

Oh GCD I would run outta spunk in no time, then i would probably fall asleep lol.  But man i've watched them on T.V and just makes me tired watching them reel in Groupers.  But i would check it off on my list to do before i die
